<varlistentry id="options.HonorConfig">
	<term>HonorConfig</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Forces AfterStep to honor a client's request to reposition itself after its window has been mapped. This is a dangerous behavior as clients do not have a reliable way of determining the best position for themselves. Window positioning should be left to AfterStep as it knows better. Opposite of IgnoreConfig.</para>
		<para>See Also: IgnoreConfig.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
